body:
Hey everyone, it did take a while to upload, as i have been working very hard to get school stuff done and get some YouTube, forum and in game time going all at once. 
But here it is :)

Please don't say stuff about spamming, I'm a little stressed out and am not in the mood for "stop spamming about YouTube" kind of stuff, because i am not spamming. The staff themselves have asked for the promotion of Avicus through YouTube and that's exactly what I'm doing, along with having some fun :)

If you enjoyed the video please be sure to like and subscribe for more videos in the series :D

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zKRSNOvVeEo

Thanks - OPTOBAT
